Low: No significant threats detected; domain is clean.
Medium: Minor issues detected; may require further review.
High: Significant threats like phishing or malware; manual review recommended.

Here are the scan results for the domain {{ $('Parse Webhook').item.json.response.view.state.values.domain_name_block.domain_name_input.value }}:

Malicious: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious }}
Suspicious: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.suspicious }}
