Harmless: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.harmless }}
Timeout: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.timeout }}
Reputation: {{ $json.data.attributes.reputation }}

Provide an overall risk rating and suggest next steps based on your analysis. Please keep it concise.

